Rating: 3
Very tasty! I changed the recipe as follows: To the chicken marinade I added ground chipotle chile for a kick. I fireroasted the red bell pepper; added 2 jalapenos (also fireroasted and chopped) and added chopped cilantro. I didn't have arugula but used Boston. I increased the oil, oregano, etc., to adequately moisten the salad ingredients. WOW! I would highly recommend for a summer evening - it's more than enough for a light dinner. Wouild be great for entertaining!